precis:
Amendment to the INCOME TAX REGULATIONS that changes the effective date of
an amendment made in 1989 which broadens the circumstances under which a
corporation receiving a dividend from a foreign affiliate out of the
foreign affiliate's taxable surplus can claim an additional amount as a
deduction in respect of the dividend.
